OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779879767
OL,3,CAmber warning issued as London
OL,4,Ctemperatures rival Caribbean hotspots
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,7,Fhas issued an amber heat health alert
OL,8,Ffor the East Midlands, West Midlands,
OL,9,Fthe east of England, London and the
OL,10,FSouth East.
OL,12,FThey are in place from 2pm on Friday
OL,13,Funtil 5pm next Wednesday and replace
OL,14,Fless severe yellow alerts which were
OL,15,Fpreviously in place.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
