OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1779879767
OL,3,CAmber warning issued as London
OL,4,Ctemperatures rival Caribbean hotspots
OL,6,FAccording to the UKHSA website, an
OL,7,Famber heat health alert means there is
OL,8,Flikely to be "a rise in deaths,
OL,9,Fparticularly among those aged 65 and
OL,10,Fover or with health conditions" and
OL,11,Fincreased demand on all health and
OL,12,Fsocial care services.
OL,14,FThis comes as the UK is forecast to
OL,15,Fsee its hottest May day on record over
OL,16,Fthe bank holiday weekend, with parts
OL,17,Fof the country set to be hotter than
OL,18,FBarbados.
OL,26,@pD@NOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
